SOIL BEHAVIOUR TYPE CHARTS

Erdi Myftaraga

1 INTRODUCTION

It can be useful sometimes to create an idea on how the CPTU measurement points of a particular site or soil unit are distributed among different SBT (Soil Behavior Type) zones. I wrote a small function to categorize CPTU data points according to the zone they plot in a few SBT charts, as listed:

  • Robertson 2009 SBT chart1;

  • Robertson 2016 SBT chart2;

  • Schneider et al. 2008 SBT chart3 (modified by Robertson 2016).
